dc_title_s: Argentina, Territorio Nacional de la Tierra del Fuego, Estrecho de le Maire, Isla de los Estados (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: compilation of hydrographic surveys done by the Servicio de Hidrografia Naval de la Armada Argentina (Naval Hydrographic Service of the Argentine Navy up to 1981). Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "Soundings in meters." "Reproduction of Argentine chart H-418, 1st edition, 1984 with modifications in accordance with agreement between the Argentine Navy Hydrographic Service and the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Argentinean copyright law applies." Includes tidal information. Sheet no. 22440. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
